As the world gets ready for Halloween, here is our selection of the best pictures during this year's celebrations 
Punky, a 5-year-old long-haired Chihuahua is seen in his owner's jacket as they attend the 42nd annual Safeway World Championship Pumpkin Weigh-Off Contest in the World Pumpkin Capital of Half Moon Bay, California Picture: AFP
